</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>Apple 修復 Studio Display Bug    用家現可更新至 iOS 15.4</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/04/12/studiodisplaybugfixed/notebook/mac-os/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=studiodisplaybugfixed</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[samuel]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Tue, 12 Apr 2022 09:53:36 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[Mac]]></category><category><![CDATA[Apple]]></category><category><![CDATA[Studio Display]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1095319</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>日前，大量 Apple Studio Display 的用家投訴無法為顯示器更新韌體。而事發一日內，Apple [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">日前，<a href="https://unwire.hk/2022/04/11/studio-display-unable-to-update/notebook/mac-os/">大量 Apple Studio Display 的用家投訴無法為顯示器更新韌體</a>。而事發一日內，Apple 已將問題修復。</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">據外國媒體 Mac Rumors 報道，這次的 Bug 是由於 Apple 在早前發佈 iOS 15.4 時，並未把 Apple Display 加入認證系統，令軟件未能成功升級 Apple Display。 在事發後，Apple 發現 Bug 並為 Apple Display 進行認證，令用戶可進行更新。</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">雖然 Apple 已在上月發佈 iOS 15.4.1 的更新，但目前 Studio Display 仍然使用 iOS 15.4。</span></p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">Apple stopped signing iOS 15.4 on 4/7</p><p>On 4/8, users started reporting that they couldn&#39;t update the Studio Display to iOS 15.4 Firmware.</p><p>As of one hour ago, iOS 15.4 Firmware for the Studio Display (Appledisplay2,1) is being signed again</p><p>The firmware update installing now! 👍 <a href="https://t.co/Sn1TyKgLkq">https://t.co/Sn1TyKgLkq</a> <a href="https://t.co/pO7rSGox1a">pic.twitter.com/pO7rSGox1a</a></p><p>&mdash; Mr. Macintosh (@ClassicII_MrMac) <a href="https://twitter.com/ClassicII_MrMac/status/1513339183808622599?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">April 11, 2022</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">而較早前 Apple 亦承諾為 Studio Display 進行更新，以改善其</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">視像鏡頭質素，但至今仍未公佈確實更新時間。</span></p><p>資料及圖片來源：<a href="https://www.macrumors.com/2022/04/11/apple-addresses-studio-display-update-errors/">MacRumors</a></p><p>unwire.hk Mewe 專頁 : <a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk">https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=24eu3BhScrk:ONXD0vYUXno:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=24eu3BhScrk:ONXD0vYUXno:qj6IDK7rITs"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=qj6IDK7rITs" border="0"></img></a>
</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>Tim Cook 全球私隱高峰會演講     4 月 12 日香港直播時間</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/04/12/timcookspeechoniapp/tech-secure/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=timcookspeechoniapp</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[samuel]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Tue, 12 Apr 2022 08:44:01 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><category><![CDATA[資訊保安]]></category><category><![CDATA[Apple]]></category><category><![CDATA[IAPP]]></category><category><![CDATA[tim cook]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1095296</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>早前國際私隱專業人士協會（IAPP）宣佈，Apple CEO Tim Cook 將在香港時間今晚（4 月 12 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">早前國際私隱專業人士協會（IAPP）宣佈，Apple CEO Tim Cook 將在香港時間今晚（4 月 12 日）九點十五分舉行的全球私隱高峰會（Global Privacy Summit）上發表演講，而會議將透過 <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Dq0fcmmzfog">YouTube 進行網上直播</a>。</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">國際私隱專業人士協會將從今晚起舉行一連三日的全球私隱高峰會，首日將由 Tim Cook 打頭陣，發表主題演講。</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">IAPP 指，一年一度的高峰會著重從實踐、政策及策略三方面探討的國際私隱安全及資料保護。</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">IAPP CEO J. Trevor Hughes 表示， Apple 是數碼經濟的龍頭，而 Tim Cook 更是資料私隱領域中領先及具影響力的聲音。他們期待這次可就私隱安全及數碼經濟等議題，與 Tim Cook 展開強而有力的對話。</span></p><p>有興趣的讀者可透過以下網址觀看直播：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Dq0fcmmzfog">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Dq0fcmmzfog</a></p><p>資料及圖片來源：<a href="https://www.macrumors.com/2022/04/05/tim-cook-to-speak-at-global-privacy-summit/">MacRumors</a></p><p>unwire.hk Mewe 專頁 : <a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk">https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=kXDadBHYGkU:-b8czYmF4-U:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=kXDadBHYGkU:-b8czYmF4-U:qj6IDK7rITs"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=qj6IDK7rITs" border="0"></img></a>
</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>Benz EQV 首款電動 MPV 七人車，續航力 378 公里 + 配 EQ 專屬 MBUX 系統</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/04/12/benzneweqvmpv/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=benzneweqvmpv</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[samuel]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Tue, 12 Apr 2022 06:07:17 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[車壇動向]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1095258</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>Mercedes-Benz 將在本月 14 日推出全新的 EQV 300 七座 MPV，主打高續航力、快速充電 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Mercedes-Benz 將在本月 14 日推出全新的 EQV 300 七座 MPV，主打高續航力、快速充電、提供 EQ 專屬的 MBUX 智能操作，屬於私人、商務通用的多功能七人車。</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">EQV 300 提供兩款型號，分別為長軸距（3,200 毫米）的 EQV 300 Long，定價低於港幣 HK$1,200,000；</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1095268" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/long-694x405.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="405" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/long-694x405.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/long-768x449.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/long.jpg 1039w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">以及特長軸距（3,430 毫米）的 EQV 300 Extra Long，定價低於港幣 HK$1,000,000。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1095269" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/extra-long-694x421.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="421" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/extra-long-694x421.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/extra-long-768x466.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/extra-long.jpg 1046w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">新車與 V-Class 相同，量產版本於西班牙北部 Vitoria 生產。車上電池可用容量達 90kWh，提供 378 km 的續航力 (WLTP)。</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">EQV 300 在行駛時也會將動力回收為電能。當加速或制動時,會將動能轉化為電能，為高壓電池充電。駕駛者可透過撥動軚盤後方左、右的撥片，增強或減少回收幅度。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1095266" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/20C0433_128-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/20C0433_128-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/20C0433_128-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/20C0433_128-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/20C0433_128-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/20C0433_128-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/20C0433_128-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">最低迴收幅度時,車輛會仿如滑行；而最高幅度時,駕駛者基本可單踏板操，在大部份情況下，動力回收時的減速力已足夠取代制動系統。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1095270" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/20C0436_006-694x472.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="472" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/20C0436_006-694x472.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/20C0436_006-1280x870.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/20C0436_006-768x522.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/20C0436_006-1536x1044.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/20C0436_006-2048x1392.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/20C0436_006-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">新車亦配備 DAuto 回收模式，自動啟動的 ECO Assistant 可協助駕駛者取得最佳節能效果。</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;"> EQV 300 同時配備車內水冷式交流電充電器，最高功率為 11 kW，方便在家或公眾充電站作交流電充電。EQV 在透過直流快速充電站以 110 kW 的功率充電時， 只需約 45 分鐘便可由 10% 充電至 80%。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1095267" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/image002-694x361.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="361" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/image002-694x361.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/image002-768x399.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/image002.jpg 816w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">EQV 300 將電能動力系統（eATS）放於流線型的車頭，前泵把設有充電插座，將電動摩打、固定齒比傳動系統、冷卻系統和電力總成藏於車頭內。其摩打輸出高達 204 hp。 </span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1095261" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/20C0247_002-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/20C0247_002-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/20C0247_002-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/20C0247_002-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/20C0247_002-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/20C0247_002-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/20C0247_002-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">其鋰電池組擺放在車底並置中，確保良好的操控表現。同時令 EQV 300 地臺平坦，車廂空間靈活多變，適合各種用途。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1095264" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/seat-1-694x455.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="455" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/seat-1-694x455.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/seat-1-1280x839.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/seat-1-768x503.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/seat-1-1536x1007.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/seat-1.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /> <img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1095265" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/seat-2-694x453.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="453" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/seat-2-694x453.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/seat-2-1280x836.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/seat-2-768x502.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/seat-2-1536x1003.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/seat-2.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">如作為家庭 MPV 時，乘客可使用中排豪華獨立座椅，第三排座椅更可作多種編排，方便出行。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1095259" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Luxury-seats-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Luxury-seats-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Luxury-seats-1200x900.jpg 1200w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Luxury-seats-768x576.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Luxury-seats-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Luxury-seats-2048x1536.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Luxury-seats-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">因應 Mercedes-EQ 而更新的 MBUX 系統亦是另一重點。在 10 吋高解像屏幕，EQ 頁面可提供多項顯示，如有關充電量、能量流和耗電量的圖像。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1095263" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/20C0433_513-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/20C0433_513-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/20C0433_513-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/20C0433_513-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/20C0433_513-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/20C0433_513-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/20C0433_513-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">屏幕亦可控制導航系統及駕駛模式。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1095262" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/mon-694x460.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="460" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/mon-694x460.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/mon-768x509.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/mon.jpg 1032w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">MBUX 系統的一大強項是以「Hey Mercedes」關鍵詞啟動的智能語音操作，支援多項資訊娛樂，如輸入目的地、撥打電話、選擇歌曲、聽取短訊、控制空氣調節、燈光系統等。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1095271" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/mon2-694x410.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="410" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/mon2-694x410.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/mon2-768x454.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/mon2.jpg 1087w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">在外形上，EQV 300 亦貫徹品牌旗下 EQ 家族的設計語言。EQV 車頭鬼面罩採用 Black </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">Panel 設計，配以鍍鉻飾條，車側配上 17 吋的輕合金輪圈。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1095272" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/20C0433_073-694x381.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="381" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/20C0433_073-694x381.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/20C0433_073-1280x703.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/20C0433_073-768x422.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/20C0433_073-1536x843.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/20C0433_073-2048x1124.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/20C0433_073-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Mercedes Benz 將在本月 14 日正式在香港展出 EQV 300，有興趣的讀者可到其<a href="https://www.mercedes-benz.com.hk/zh_HK/passengercars/mercedes-benz-cars/models/eqv/explore.html">官網</a>查看更多。</p><p>資料及圖片來源：Mercedes-Benz</p><p>unwire.hk Mewe 專頁 : <a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk">https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
